    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Minimum age 18 years

          -  Indication for cementless hip arthroplasty with acetabular defects that need Allograft
             or titanium augment

          -  Patient consent for study participation

          -  Physical and mental willingness to participate in the follow-ups

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient not available for follow-up

          -  Increased anesthetics risks for the patient according to the &quot;American Society of
             Anesthesiology&quot;: ASA IV

          -  Tumor

          -  Alcohol- or Drug abuse

          -  Permanent cortisone therapy

          -  Clinically relevant infection

          -  (Planned) pregnancy
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
